        </item>
        <item>
            <title>即溶咖啡被驗出含「壯陽藥」 HKTVmall ：「已即時下架貨品」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/hktvmall/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hktvmall</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/hktvmall/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 09:29:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HKTVmall]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[昔多芬]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[東革阿里即溶咖啡]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272381</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">衞生署表示，一款名為「東革阿里即溶咖啡」的產品被檢出含有受管制的處方藥物「昔多芬」，並呼籲市民切勿購買或服用此產品。網購平台 HKTVmall 回覆媒體查詢時確認，該平台有一間商户曾售賣此產品，但已迅速下架。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272384 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-694x186.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="186" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-694x186.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲HKTVmall 已下架「東革阿里即溶咖啡」（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E6%9C%9B%E6%99%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/B0631001/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81/%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9/%E6%9D%B1%E9%9D%A9%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A18%E5%8C%85/p/B0631001_S_4897136810032">HKTVmall</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「東革阿里即溶咖啡」早前被發現產品含有「昔多芬」，HKTVmall 得悉貨品在平台上放售，已立即下架，並會通知曾購買的顧客進行酌情處理及退款。HKTVmall 強調，平台內設有品質監察部門，訂立嚴謹商户準則，並定期抽查商户商品，以確保產品合乎法規。一旦發現違規商品，會立即下架並對商户處以罰款或終止合作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272385 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mfile_1776925_1_2024-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mfile_1776925_1_2024-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mfile_1776925_1_2024.jpg 1208w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「東革阿里即溶咖啡」早前被發現產品含有壯陽藥「昔多芬」（圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1776925-20241030.htm">RTHK</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「昔多芬」為一種常用於治療勃起功能障礙的藥物，其副作用包括頭痛、低血壓、頭暈等，對心臟病患者尤其危險，如與治療心絞痛的藥物如「硝酸甘油」共同使用，可能導致血壓驟降，造成嚴重的健康風險。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">有網民對事件作出諷刺反應，戲稱「買咖啡送偉哥（壯陽藥）」、「呼籲完銷量好咗」，並在討論區留言「即刻掃貨」等。HKTVmall 表示會繼續密切監察，並配合政府檢查和規範。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1272388" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2-694x362.png" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2-694x362.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272387 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-602x580.png" alt="" width="602" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-602x580.png 602w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1.png 666w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 602px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民戲稱「買咖啡送偉哥（壯陽藥）」、「呼籲完銷量好咗」及「即刻掃貨」（圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3813005/page/1">LIHKG</a>）</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1776925-20241030.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3813005/page/1">LIHKG</a>、<a href="https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E6%9C%9B%E6%99%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/B0631001/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81/%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9/%E6%9D%B1%E9%9D%A9%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A18%E5%8C%85/p/B0631001_S_4897136810032">HKTVmall</a>、<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20241031/s00001/1730348470085/hktvmall%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E5%90%AB%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1-%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E6%9B%BE%E5%94%AE">明報</a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2032762/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA-%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E8%B2%B7-HKTV-mall%E5%8D%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%88%B2%E8%AC%94%E6%9B%B2%E7%B7%9A%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3-%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8">星島日報</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
